<p>
The situation in the global economy is as follows: the banking system, consumption, production - all ready to emerge. Moreover, it will develop from any disturbance. The phase transition can occur from any perturbations, said one the most independent - from mainstream cliches and theories - economic analyst Stepan Demura. In a lecture he recently read has everything from forecasts on gold, oil and the ruble to the recipes of what to do with the economy and finances.
